description.english: You've started this game. Let's run!
You're so brave, went out of your house
You went to the tech store. I'm not sure you have enough money.
You were doing strange things, so the decided to put you here.
You was walking with bottle of vodka… and now you're here.
Half of Russia looks like it, you know?
THERE IS SO HOT I AM GOING TO DIE
Such a good drink, brought you to heavens.
You're thinking that it's good to walk sometimes.
Walking is definitely your kind of thing.
You've lost your home, but in the street everybody respects you.
This smartphones, 4K TV's and gaming PC's. Probably interesting.
You don't have enough money to buy it. So you've stolen it.
It's nice place to live. Air is warmed by this PC's.
Something changed in your brain. You've started talking strangely.
There's too mush syringes and pills. You need to stop.
That's what vodka makes with people.
You didn't start the fight. This guy just smashed you in the face.
Wrestling is hour hobby. And you're drinking every day.
You've stopped wrestling and started deboshiring. Police don't like it.
People are throwing away so many things. Maybe you'll find something.
You've found some clothes. Maybe sell it on barakholka?
If you're living near a trash heap then you're definitely a bomj.
You've done many bad things in your life. You must go to hell.
It's not your first time being in hell. You're getting used to it.
Hell seems to be your place. You're the king here. The Devil.
You've done many good things. You deserved a place in heavens.
You've helped many people there, in heavens. They're calling you Angel.
You're the best. Everybody knows you. You're the God.
